\c 8
\s Vanezvuru zvina vanopiwa zvokudya naJesu
\p
\v 1 Namazuva iwayo zvakwakanga kune gurumwandira guru, vasina zvavangadya, akadanira vadzidzi vake \add kwaari\add*, akati kwavari:
\v 2 Ndinetsitsi navanhu vazhinji, nokuti atova mazuva matatu avakagara neni vasina zvavangadya.
\v 3 Kana ndikavaendisa kumusha kwavo vasina kudya, vachaziya panzira; vamwe vavo vanobva kure.
\v 4 Vadzidzi vake vakamupindura, \add vakati\add*: Munhu ungawanepiko murenje muno, zvingwa zvingagutisa vanhu ava?
\v 5 Akavabvunza, \add akati\add*: Munezvingwa zvinganiko? Vakati: Zvinomwe.
\v 6 Zvino akaraira vanhu vazhinji kuti vagare pasi, akatora zvingwa zvinomwe, akavonga, akazvimedura, ndokupa vadzidzi vake, kuti vaise pamberi \add pavo\add*; vakazviisa pamberi pavazhinji.
\v 7 Vuye vakanga vanehove duku shomanene; zvino akadziropafadza, akati zviiswe vo pamberi \add pavo\add*.
\v 8 Vakadya, vakaguta, ndokuvunganidza zvimedu zvakasara, matengu manomwe.
\v 9 Avo vakadya vainge vaiva zvuru zvina; akavaendisa.
\v 10 Pakarepo akapinda mugwa navadzidzi vake, akasvika kumativi enyika yeDharimanuta.
\s Jesu unoramba kuratidza chiratidzo.
\p
\v 11 Zvino vaFarisi vakabuda, vakatanga kupikisana naye, vachitsvaka kwaari chiratidzo chinobva kudenga, vachimuidza.
\v 12 Akagomera zvikuru pamweya wake, akati: Rudzi urwu runotsvakireiko chiratidzo? Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Hakuna chiratidzo chungapiwa rudzi urwu.
\v 13 Ipapo akavasiya, akapinda zve mugwa, akayambukira mhiri.
\s Jesu unodudzira shoko rembiriso yavaFarisi navaSajusi.
\p
\v 14 Zvino vakanga vakanganwa kutora zvingwa; vakanga vasinezvingwa, asi chimwe bedzi.
\v 15 Zvino akavaraira, akati: Rangarirai muchenjere, mbiriso yavaFarisi nembiriso yaHerodhe.
\v 16 Vakarangana vakati: Nokuti hatine zvingwa.
\v 17 Zvino Jesu achizviziva, akati kwavari: Munorangana nemhaka yeiko kuti hamunezingwa? Hamuzivi, nokunzwisisa here? Moyo yenyu ichiri mikukutu here?
\v 18 Zvamunameso, hamuvoni here? Zvamunenzeve, hamunzwi here? Hamurangariri here?
\v 19 Musi wandakamedurira vanezvuru zvishanu zvingwa zvishanu, makanonga matengu azere manganiko nezvimedu? Vakati kwaari: Gumi namaviri.
\v 20 Nomusi wandakamedurira vanezvuru zvina zvingwa zvinomwe, makanonga matengu manganiko akazadzwa nezvimedu? Vakati: Manomwe.
\v 21 Akati kwavari: Nemhaka yeyi musinganzwisisi?
\s Jesu unosvinudza bofu paBhetisaidha
\p
\v 22 Zvino wakasvika Bhetisaidha; vakavuya nebofu kwaari, vakakumbira zvikuru kwaari, kuti amunyangate.
\v 23 akabata ruvoko rwebofu, akamubudisira kunze komusha, ndokupfira mate pameso ake, akaisa mavoko pamusoro pake, akamubvunza kana achivona chinhu.
\v 24 Iye akatarira, akati: Ndinovona vanhu vakaita semiti, vachifamba.
\v 25 Mushure maizvozvo akaisazve mavoko pamusoro pameso ake akamutaridza kudenga, akaporeswa akavona zvose zvakanaka.
\v 26 Akamuendesa kumba kwake achiti: Usatongopinda mumusha kana kuvudza munhu mumusha.
\s Petro unopupura kuti Jesu ndiye Kristu.
\p
\v 27 Zvino Jesu akabuda navadzidzi vake vakaenda kumisha yeKesaria Firipo; munzira akabvunza vadzidzi vake akati kwavari: Vanhu vanoti ndini aniko?
\v 28 Vakapindura \add vachiti\add* : Johwani Mubhabhatidzi; vamwe, Eria, vamwezve, mumwe wavaporofita.
\v 29 Zvino akati kwavari: Ko imi munoti ndini ani? Petro akapindura, akati kwaari: Ndimi Kristu.
\v 30 Akavaraira zvikuru kuti varege kuzivisa munhu pamusoro pake.
\v 31 Zvino akatanga kuvadzidzisa kuti Mwanakomana womunhu unofanira kutambudzika zvizhinji nokurashwa navakuru, navaprista vakuru, navanyori, avurawe, amukezve mushure mamazuva matatu.
\v 32 Akataura shoko iro pachena. Zvino Petro akaenda naye parutivi, akatanga kumuraira.
\v 33 Asi iye wakatendevuka, ndokutarira vadzidzi vake, akaraira Petro akati: Ibva shure kwangu, Satani, nokuti haurangariri zvinhu zvaMwari, asi zvinhu zvavanhu.
\s Kutevera Jesu
\p
\v 34 Zvino wakadanira kwaari vanhu va zhinji navadzidzi vake, akati kwavari: Kana munhu achida kuvuya shure kwangu, ngaazvirambe, asimudze muchinjikwa wake, anditevere.
\v 35 Nokuti aninani unoda kuponesa vupenyu bwake, ucharashikirwa nabwo, asi aninani unorashikirwa novupenyu bwake nokuda kwangu nokweevhangeri, ndiye uchavuponeswa.
\v 36 Nokuti munhu uchagobatsirweiko kana awana nyika yose akarashikirwa nomweya wake?
\v 37 Nokuti munhu ucharipeiko kuti adzikinure mweya wake?
\v 38 Nokuti aninani unonyara pamusoro pangu namashoko angu parudzi urwu rwovupombwe nokutadza, Mwanakomana womhunhu uchanyaravo pamusoro pake, musi waanovuya nokubwinya kwake naBaba vake navatumwa vatsvene.
